<item><title>Air Compressor Skid</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Supply and delivery of the items below<br /><br />Two (2) x 100% duty fully redundant air compressors are available to automatically maintain Compressed Air System (CAS) operation in the event of single air compressor failure. <br /><br />The Compressed Air System is capable of being operated and controlled from a local control panel and from the plant control system. <br /><br />Condensed water from the compressed air system package is drained via gravity to the skid edge boundary and then shall be connected into the nearest oil wastewater drain. <br /><br />The key elements of the Compressed Air System include, but not limited to the following: <br /><br />•	Two (2) x 100% duty (1 Working and 1 Standby), air cooled, oil free rotary screw type air compressor <br /><br />o	Air compressor with intake filtration <br /><br />o	Compressors associated with intercoolers, aftercoolers, and Oil filters (as applicable) <br /><br />•	Wet air receiver tanks (1 x 100% duty) – if applicable. <br /><br />•	Twin tower regen...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Monadelphous<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 04/Aug/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517742<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Gas Energy, Infrastructure, Equipment, Mechanical Plant, Equip, Services, Plant & Equipment - Purchase<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 0]]></description>
