<item><title>Sippy Downs Campus Building Refurbishments</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The tender comprises of two scopes, with separable portions, which University Sunshine Coast may elect to award to one supplier, or separate the scopes based on value delivery and program requirements. The tender is set out as:<br /><br />PART B.1 – BUILDING B REFURBISHMENT - 1 separable portion<br /><br />The University of the Sunshine Coast (UniSC) invites qualified contractors to tender for the delivery of the Building B Fresh Project at the Sippy Downs Campus under a Design and Construct contract. The project delivers a comprehensive program of internal and external refurbishment works to Building B - the University’s original and historically significant campus building.<br /><br />The successful supplier will be responsible for delivering the required works in accordance with UniSC requirements and the issued design documentation, within an operational university environment. The works will require effective coordination, staging and interface management, including alignment with early works delivered s...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> UniSC<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 27/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517584<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 18]]></description>
