<item><title>EOI 18.26 Pavement Strengthening, Apron Expansion and Airfield Ground Lighting – Onslow</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Shire of Ashburton (the Principal) is seeking Expressions of Interest (EOI) from suitably qualified and experienced construction contractors for the delivery of the Onslow Airport Runway Pavement Strengthening and Aircraft Capacity Expansion Project (the Project).<br /><br />The Project forms a critical infrastructure upgrade to support the continued safe operation of Onslow Airport and accommodate larger Code C aircraft, ensuring long-term serviceability and regional connectivity.<br /><br />This EOI is a pre-qualification and shortlisting process intended to identify contractors with the demonstrated capability, capacity, and relevant experience to be invited to participate in a subsequent Request for Tender (RFT) for the construction works.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Shire of Ashburton<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 07/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+08:00) Perth time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517497<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Construction & Operation, Engineer, Research, Tech services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
