<item><title>T27004 – Tree Root Management Service</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Contract No. T27004 – Tree Root Management Service<br /><br />The City of Stonnington manages a substantial and diverse urban tree population located within parks, facilities, streetscapes and other open spaces. To ensure community safety, asset protection and long-term tree health, the City of Stonnington is seeking to appoint a panel of suitably qualified and experienced suppliers to provide reactive Tree Root Management Services. The panel will support the timely and effective delivery of services in response to identified tree root issues and associated risks. This procurement will ensure consistent service delivery, regulatory compliance, effective risk management, and the ongoing amenity and environmental value of Stonnington’s urban forest.<br /><br />A tender briefing will be held on Tuesday 28 July 2026 at 10:00am. Please refer to RFT documents for further details.<br /><br />NOTE: The Vendor Panel online forum closes five business days prior to the abovementioned tender closing date. Council reserve...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Stonnington<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Aug/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517246<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Horticulture & Arboriculture<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 1]]></description>
