<guid isPermaLink="false">dbaf059d6bf84329a8e0d276ab19a7d9</guid>
<pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
<category>Horticulture &amp; Arboriculture</category>
</item>
<item><title>T26022 – Open Space Maintenance and Sportsground Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Contract No. T26022 – Open Space Maintenance and Sportsground Services <br /><br />The City of Stonnington manages an extensive network of parks, sportsgrounds, streetscapes and community recreation assets that support high levels of daily community use. These open spaces accommodate organised sport, informal recreation, events and passive enjoyment, and include natural turf sportsgrounds, cricket practice facilities, playgrounds, garden beds, nature strips and road reserve vegetation.<br /><br />The City of Stonnington is seeking a suitably qualified contractor to maintain safety, presentation and asset performance standards, Council is seeking an integrated service provider to deliver routine mowing and turf care, cricket wicket preparation, litter collection, playground inspections and minor repairs, dog bag replenishment, nature strip reinstatement and vegetation management. This contract will ensure consistent service delivery, asset longevity and high-quality public amenity across the municipality.<br /...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Stonnington<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Aug/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517387<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Cleaning Services, Equip, Supplies, Horticulture & Arboriculture, Real Estate & Property Services, Sport, Recreation Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 1]]></description>
