<item><title>TEN/3015 Supply of Promotional Printing Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Bundaberg Regional Council is a local government organisation dedicated to serving the diverse needs of<br /><br />our community. Our council encompasses a wide range of services and activities, and effective<br /><br />communication is vital to ensure transparent and efficient operations. We recognise the significance of<br /><br />quality print materials in conveying key messages and promoting engagement with our various initiatives,<br /><br />projects, and services.<br /><br />Council's requirements include the production of high-quality printed materials such as brochures,<br /><br />posters, corflutes, newsletters, promotional materials, and other communications assets.<br /><br />The successful Respondent will be responsible for meeting our printing needs promptly, maintaining a<br /><br />high standard of quality, and demonstrating innovation in production concepts.<br /><br />We anticipate a long-term partnership that fosters creativity, collaboration, and efficiency in delivering<br /><br />outstand...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Bundaberg Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 11/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516948<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Paper Materials & Products<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 5]]></description>
