<item><title>T27005 – Consulting Arborist Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Contract No. T27005 – Consulting Arborist Services<br /><br />To ensure community safety, asset protection, and long-term tree health, the City of Stonnington requires a panel of suitably qualified and experienced Consulting Arborists to support the broad and varied Tree Management service delivery. This contractor panel will ensure consistent service delivery, regulatory compliance, risk management, and the sustained amenity and environmental value of Stonnington’s urban forest.<br /><br />A tender briefing will be held on Tuesday 28 July 2026 at 11:00am. Please refer to RFT documents for further details.<br /><br />NOTE: The Vendor Panel online forum closes five business days prior to the abovementioned tender closing date. Council reserves the right not to accept the lowest or any Tender, or part thereof. Tenders received after the closing time will not be considered.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Stonnington<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Aug/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517258<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Architecture, Design, Planning, Horticulture & Arboriculture<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 1]]></description>
