<item><title>Provision and Installation of Two Autoclaves</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Supply, Delivery and Installation of Two (2) Laboratory Autoclaves<br /><br />1. Introduction<br /><br />QIMR Berghofer Medical Research Institute invites suitably qualified and experienced suppliers to submit an Offer for the supply, delivery, installation, commissioning, and training associated with two (2) Laboratory Autoclaves.<br /><br />The autoclaves will be utilised as part of QIMR Berghofer's ongoing laboratory operations and will primarily be used for the sterilisation and treatment of laboratory equipment, consumables, and biological waste.<br /><br />2. Project Overview<br /><br />The purpose of this Invitation to Offer (ITO) is to source two (2) Laboratory Autoclaves that meet the operational, safety, and compliance requirements of QIMR Berghofer's PC3 laboratory environment.<br /><br />The successful supplier will be responsible for providing a complete turnkey solution, including all costs associated with:<br /><br />Supply of two (2) laboratory autoclaves.<br /><br />Freight and transportation...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> QIMR Berghofer Medical Research Institute<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 14/Aug/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517477<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Lab, Measure, Observe & Test Equip, Medical Equipment. & Supplies<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 8]]></description>
