<item><title>Cleaning Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Council is calling for responses from suitably experienced and qualified Contractors to provide services (Services) within the Penrith Local Government Area in relation to Cleaning Services for Community Facilities (Project), as further described in Attachment [3] of this RFT – Contract Scope of Services. 	The Scope of Services will involve cleaning designated community facilities across four (4) Categories of service. <br /><br />The Categories include Community Centres, Halls, Neighbourhood Centres, Youth Centres, Senior’s Centres, Libraries, Leisure Centres, Childcare Facilities, and St Marys Queen Street Administration Building.<br /><br />The 4 Categories of facility types as specified:<br /><br />(a)	Community Facilities <br /><br />(i)	Community Centres<br /><br />(ii)	Halls<br /><br />(iii)	Neighbourhood centres <br /><br />(iv)	Youth Centres<br /><br />(v)	Senior’s Centres<br /><br />(b)	Leisure Centres<br /><br />(c)	Childcare Facilities <br /><br />(d)	Libraries & Administration Building<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Penrith City Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 11/Sep/2026 03:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP517412<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Cleaning Services, Equip, Supplies<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
