<item><title>27_003 Design and Rectification of Two Landslip Sites for Southern Downs Regional Council</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Dear Valued Suppliers<br /><br />Southern Downs Regional Council (“Council”) is seeking a suitably qualified contractor/s to provide design, and construction works for two landslip sites as part of Council’s 2025 DRFA Program. <br /><br />The sites are located east of Warwick in the Swanfel area. <br /><br />The sites are located on Days Road, Swanfels and Top Swanfels Road, Swanfels. Refer to Attachments C and D for location maps.<br /><br />A site assessment and option analysis of the sites has been undertaken by Engeo (Australia) Pty Ltd through their Brisbane office. Refer to Attachments A and B. <br /><br />Works are targeted for completion by 12 March 2027.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Southern Downs Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 25/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516905<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 10]]></description>
