<category>Construction &amp; Operation</category>
</item>
<item><title>TEN/3014 Register of Pre-Qualified Suppliers for Graphic Design</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Bundaberg Regional Council delivers a broad range of services, programs, projects, events, facilities, and community facing activities. Effective communication is essential to ensure transparency, accessibility, public awareness, and community engagement.<br /><br />Well-designed visual communication material supports Council’s ability to present information clearly, professionally, and consistently across multiple channels. This includes print, digital, social media, signage, advertising, reports, community engagement collateral, campaign material, project branding, and internal corporate communication material.<br /><br />To continue providing the above, Council has identified a need to outsource some graphic design requests. Any outsourcing will be in support to Council’s Communications team, and requests will come only from this team.<br /><br />To ensure appropriate flexibility, capacity, value for money, and access to a broader range of creative styles and technical skills a panel model has been determi...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Bundaberg Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 04/Aug/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516854<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Graphical, Photographic & Art<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
