<item><title>C26-141 Underground Drainage Pipe Relining Works - Eucalypt Court and Candlebark Court, Riddells Creek</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The scope of this contract includes the investigation of the existing drainage pipeline at Eucalypt Court and Candlebark Court, Riddells Creek, followed by the rehabilitation of the existing stormwater pipe using trenchless relining methods, including Cured-In-Place Pipe (CIPP) or other Council-approved systems. The contractor shall deliver all necessary works to assess, prepare, and reline the pipeline to meet required performance and durability standards.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Macedon Ranges Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 11/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516661<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation, Water & Sewage<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 8]]></description>
