<item><title>ITT2563 Supply &amp; Installation of Cell 6 and Cell 7 Landfill Liner System Nambour Landfill Expansion</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Tenders are invited for the supply, installation, testing and certification of the Cell 6 and Cell 7 Sidewall Liner System for the Nambour Landfill Expansion Project located at 18 Cooney Road, Bli Bli. <br /><br />This contract is limited to the supply and installation of the geosynthetic liner components (HDPE geomembrane and protection geotextile) for Cell 6 Sidewall Liner Lifts 2 and 3 and Cell 7 baseliner and piggyback lift 1. <br /><br />Council will be completing the civil construction and liner surface elements to the liner receiving surface specified levels and tolerances. <br /><br />This is a lump sum contract. It is anticipated that the liner material installation will commence on 1 December 2026, with an anticipated practical completion 30 June 2027.<br /><br />The successful contractor is to provide all materials, plant and labour, and to perform all necessary operations to ensure proper completion of the works associated with the Contract.<br /><br />A site information session will be held in ac...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Sunshine Coast Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 11/Aug/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516391<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation, Waste Management & Landfill<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 12]]></description>
