<item><title>T27003 – Street and Park Tree Pruning and Maintenance Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Contract No. T27003 – Street and Park Tree Pruning and Maintenance Services<br /><br />The City of Stonnington is seeking a suitably qualified and experienced specialised tree management contractor to undertake biennial programmed street tree pruning and maintenance, reactive tree pruning and maintenance, programmed topiary tree pruning and programmed parks and facilities tree pruning and maintenance to<br /><br />ensure consistent service delivery, regulatory compliance, risk management, and the sustained amenity and environmental value of Stonnington’s urban forest.<br /><br />A tender briefing will be held on Wednesday 22 July 2026 at 12:00pm. Please refer to RFT documents for further details.<br /><br />NOTE: The Vendor Panel online forum closes five business days prior to the abovementioned tender closing date. Council reserves the right not to accept the lowest or any Tender, or part thereof. Tenders received after the closing time will not be considered.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Stonnington<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 03/Aug/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516492<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Horticulture & Arboriculture<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
