<item><title>TRC000535 Preferred Supplier Arrangement for liquid waste collection and transportation</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Council is seeking to establish a preferred supplier arrangement for liquid waste collection and transportation within council’s waste handling facilities, excluding chemical toilet waste.<br /><br />The successful offerors are required to carry out the collection, transportation, and disposal of the liquid waste from designated council sites to either Wetalla WRF or other designated unloading points. The services are to be spread periodically throughout the course of this contract and the servicing will be carried out on a nominated frequency or on an “as and when required basis”.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Toowoomba Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 04/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516498<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Waste Management & Landfill, Water & Sewage<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 7]]></description>
