<item><title>Professional Services for 2026 Planning Scheme Review</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Council is seeking quotations from suitably qualified and experienced planning consultants to undertake the 2026 Planning Scheme Review.<br /><br />The review will assess the effectiveness of the current Planning Scheme, identify opportunities for improvement, and ensure it continues to support Council's strategic planning objectives and complies with legislative requirements.<br /><br />Respondents are required to submit a detailed methodology outlining their proposed approach to delivering the Planning Scheme Review, including a project plan, key milestones, proposed timeframes, and milestone-based fees.<br /><br />Council looks forward to receiving submissions from experienced consultants with demonstrated expertise in strategic planning and planning scheme reviews.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Central Goldfields Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516521<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Architecture, Design, Planning, Business & Administrative Services, Management Advisory Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
