<item><title>Wet Weather Items</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Queensland Police Service (QPS) is releasing an updated Expressions of Interest (EOI) for suitable suppliers to participate in an upcoming Request for Quote (RFQ) that will be released following this EOI process. Suppliers are invited to respond to the two questions as long as they are able to comply with the specifications outlined in Attachments A, B and C. Please note there have been additions to the standards the garments are required to meet. <br /><br />QPS requires all Police Officers (PO), Police Liaison Officers (PLO) and Protective Services Officers (PSO) to be provided with a suitable reflectorised raincoat and QPS officers with additional Wet Weather (WW) trousers. In addition, QPS requires all Motorcycle Riders to be provided with suitable reflectorised WW jackets and trousers.<br /><br />The raincoat and trousers for PO, PLO and PSO’s as well as the raincoat and trousers for Motorcycle Riders are required to provide protection and comfort from wet (rainy) conditions and will be worn in extre...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Queensland Police Service<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516506<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Clothing & Safety Equipment<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
