<item><title>RFT26-014 Urban Road Resurfacing</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Tenders closing on 5 August 2026 are invited for a suitably qualified Contractor(s) to resurface sections of Bussell Highway, Queen Elizabeth Avenue, Fairway Drive and Layman Road in the City of Busselton with new asphalt while maintaining existing surface levels.<br /><br />Bussell Highway is a dual-lane arterial road that carries a significant volume of traffic. This high-volume urban corridor demands minimal disruption during construction and requires a durable asphalt surfacing solution capable of withstanding sustained traffic loading, including heavy vehicles. <br /><br />Due to the nature of the Works, the Contractor shall coordinate with road users, residents, and other stakeholders, and allow for interfaces with other parties where required within the work area.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Busselton<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 05/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+08:00) Perth time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515858<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 9]]></description>
