<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Department of Transport and Main Roads, North Coast Region, is seeking proposals for South Pine Road and Eatons Crossing Road, upgrade intersection. The project works include:<br /><br />- Pavement widening<br /><br />- Asphalt resurfacing<br /><br />- Traffic signal modifications<br /><br />- Road lighting modifications and installation<br /><br />Contractors with TMR prequalification Major R3, Minor A3 and Financial F10 and above are invited to tender.<br /><br />Tenderers are advised the Queensland Code and Guidelines apply to this tender.<br /><br />Only TMR prequalified eligible tenderers will be given access to the Tender Documents via the QBuild eTender website: https://etender.hpw.qld.gov.au/. Prequalified tenderers are to email NC_Procurement_Inbox@tmr.qld.gov.au to gain access to the tender documents.<br /><br />Note: Due to an undeliverable message some users are experiencing, please type the email address into your email rather than using the copy and paste function.<br /><br />Tender submissi...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Department of Transport and Main Roads-North Coast<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 11/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516113<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 0]]></description>
