<item><title>Two Way Radio Equipment</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The City of Vincent is seeking to engage a suitably qualified and experienced organisation to replace and upgrade the existing two way radio equipment at the City. In 2018, the City awarded a four year contract for the supply and installation of a two way radio solution following a competitive tender process. Handsets and equipment associated with this contract are now 8 years old and at end of operational life.<br /><br />Please refer to the attached Request for Tender document for all information including how to respond.<br /><br />The closing time and date for all submissions is 2:00pm (WST) Wednesday 12 August 2026.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Vincent<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 12/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+08:00) Perth time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515677<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Jeremy Chalmers Email: jeremy.chalmers@vincent.wa.gov.au Tel: +61892736517<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Defence & Law Enforcement, Indust. Automat'n, Process Control, IT & Telecomms, Railway, Tramway and Track<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
