<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> QUILPIE SHIRE COUNCIL invites tenders from suitably qualified tenderers for the construction of civil infrastructure associated with the Quilpie Industrial Subdivision.<br /><br />The works include earthworks, road construction, water reticulation, telecommunications pits and Pipes and associated civil infrastructure required to service the new industrial lots and delivery of subdivision infrastructure.<br /><br />Electrical infrastructure is excluded from this Contract and will be delivered under a separate contract. Sewer infrastructure is not included in the Works.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Quilpie Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516001<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 17]]></description>
