<item><title>Mount Isa Hospital Lifts Project</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> North West Hospital and Health Service (the Customer) invites tenders from suitably qualified and experienced contractors to upgraded lifts servicing Block C at the Mount isa Hospital (the Project).<br /><br />The Project delivers the construction of new lifts servicing Block C at Mount Isa Hospital. A support structure and lift are being installed between Blocks B and C. Once complete, the current double lift arrangement in Block C will be modified and replaced with a single larger capacity lift.<br /><br />Maintenance beyond the maintenance period (see specification), is not included in the scope. However, pricing for this is being requested as an option for the supplier to complete for consideration by NWHHS for possible incorporation into the scope of work. If deemed value for money by the Principal, a separate contract or contract conditions for maintenance may be executed with the successful supplier for this additional work.<br /><br />The following works are also being delivered within the package of ...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> North West Hospital and Health Service<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 13/Aug/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP516050<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint.<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
