<item><title>RPQS 56-26 Design, Creative, Digital, Multimedia, Print &amp; Marketing Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Gladstone Regional Council (GRC) seeks to establish a Register of Pre-Qualified Suppliers (RPQS) comprising suitably qualified Service Providers for a range of digital media services.<br /><br />GRC periodically engages suitably experienced and qualified Service Providers to provide professional digital media, design, marketing, and print services to support GRC’s internal and external communication objectives. These services support a wide range of GRC activities, including community engagement, corporate communications, public awareness campaigns, events, and branding initiatives.<br /><br />The services may be required on an as-needed basis and may include, but are not limited to, the following categories:<br /><br />•	Graphic Design Support Services<br /><br />Provision of creative design services to support GRC’s visual communication needs, including the development of artwork and layouts for print, digital, signage, and online platforms, in accordance with GRC’s branding and communication objectives.<br...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Gladstone Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 28/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515547<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Advertising and Media Services, Graphical, Photographic & Art, Marketing & Communications, Printing & Distribution Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 12]]></description>
