<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Council is seeking to appoint a panel of suppliers to provide swimwear and aquatic merchandise for retail sale across Leisure Centres. The contract will support retail operations, enhance customer experience, and ensure reliable access to high-quality swim products. The objectives of this service is to ; <br /><br />•	Provide a consistent and high-quality retail offering<br /><br />•	Enhance customer experience across leisure centres<br /><br />•	Establish a flexible panel of suppliers<br /><br />•	Maximise value through competitive pricing and supply models<br /><br />See Scope in Request for Tender document for more information.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Sutherland Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515310<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Sport, Recreation Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
