<item><title>Neuro Wellness Hubs</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> This Invitation to Offer is for the establishment of eight (8) Neuro Wellness Hubs (Hubs), providing a coordinated model of care for Queenslanders experiencing neurological health conditions, and the delivery of the neuro community navigator program.<br /><br />The Neuro Wellness Hubs will provide a community-based space to deliver neuro wellness services, resources and information to people with neurological conditions (and their families/support network), and complement the services provided by acute speciality teams, general practice and other primary care services.<br /><br />The neuro community navigators’ program will support system navigation by connecting people with neurological conditions to broader systems including (but not limited to) the National Disability Insurance Scheme (NDIS), My Aged Care, Medicare and mental health services. <br /><br />The Queensland Government is seeking the establishment of Hubs in the following regions:<br /><br />• Townsville (Townsville Hospital and Health Service (...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Queensland Health<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 03/Aug/2026 10:00 AM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP514561<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Community & Social Services, Healthcare Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 5]]></description>
