<item><title>MidCoast Council - Forster Sewage Treatment Plant Admin Building Refurbishment</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Forster Sewage Treatment Plant Administration Building is occupied by MidCoast Council Sewage Treatment Plant operators and support functions.<br /><br />Forster Sewage Treatment Plant is located at Sweet Pea Road Forster 2428<br /><br />A summary of the project refurbishment scope includes: <br /><br />- Removal of redundant laboratory equipment – fume cupboards. <br /><br />- Removal of redundant extraction fan systems. <br /><br />- Removal of redundant ducted air-conditioning. <br /><br />- Removal and patching of internal roof vents. <br /><br />- Removal and replacement of external roof sheeting, gutters, flashings and downpipes. <br /><br />- Removal and replacement of water damaged internal roof linings. <br /><br />- Removal and replacement of internal lights.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> MidCoast Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Jul/2026 03:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513888<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint.<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 9]]></description>
