<category>ELEC, Lighting, Equip &amp; Services</category>
<category>Power Generation, Trans &amp; Distrib.</category>
</item>
<item><title>Solar &amp; Battery Installation</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Barcaldine Regional Council (BRC) is implementing renewable energy generation and energy <br /><br />efficiency measures to reduce council’s carbon emissions and reduce electricity costs across <br /><br />council-owned sites. This request for tender (RFT) seeks an end-to-end service provider to <br /><br />design, supply, install, commission and hand over solar photovoltaic (PV) systems, and where <br /><br />applicable battery energy storage systems (BESS), across nominated BRC facilities.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Barcaldine Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 26/Jul/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513994<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Power Generation, Trans & Distrib.<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
