<item><title>T-MSC2026-08 - Kuranda WTP Intake Works</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Mareeba Shire Council invites tenders from suitably qualified respondents for rectification works of the Kuranda Water Treatment Plant which was damaged following the Tropical Cyclone Jasper, associated rainfall and flooding, 13-28 December 2023 weather event. Works include construction of new water inlet pipework, connections and accompanied anchorage systems. The scope of services is described in more detail in the attached documents.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Mareeba Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 28/Jul/2026 11:00 AM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513903<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Water & Sewage<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 17]]></description>
