<item><title>Kroombit Dam Passive Dowelling Works</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Sunwater is seeking an Offer for the provision of drilling and civil construction services to undertake passive dowelling works at Kroombit Dam. The remedial works require passive dowels to be drilled from the top of the spillway crest through the conventional vibrated concrete (CVC) ogee cap into the main roller compacted concrete (RCC) sections of the spillway along the entire length. The engagement will be for a lump sum, fixed price. The works will be construct only under the AS2124.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> SunWater<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Jul/2026 10:00 AM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP472902<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Steven Garrick Email: steven.garrick@sunwater.com.au Tel: 0731200242<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 9]]></description>
