<item><title>Recreation &amp; Community Facility at Cowandilla Reserve (CWT202600618)</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The City of West Torrens (the Council) invites Tenders from Tenderers for the provision of the new Recreation and Community Facility at Cowandilla Reserve (the Works).<br /><br />The Cowandilla Reserve redevelopment project aims to deliver a contemporary, multi-purpose community and recreational facility that will meet the current and future needs of the growing West Torrens community.<br /><br />Note: Compliance with the Council's online tool for managing contractors' Work Health and Safety systems is a mandatory requirement. Please refer to Schedule 6 for further information. Failure to comply with this requirement will result in a non-conforming submission and will not considered during the evaluation process.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of West Torrens<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+09:30) Adelaide time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP511921<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 10]]></description>
